DTSTAMP:20260314T204517Z
DTSTART:20260502T230000Z
DTEND:20260503T004000Z
SUMMARY:Maybe Happy Ending
LOCATION:Belasco Theatre, 111 West 44th Street, New York NY 10036
DESCRIPTION:<p>Winner of 6 Tony Awards, including Best Musical, <em>Maybe
  Happy Ending</em> tells the deeply human story of a chance encounter that
  sparks connection, adventure, and maybe even love. Helmed by Tony
  Award-winning director Michael Arden (<em>Parade</em>), <em>Maybe Happy
  Ending</em> has been called &ldquo;Astonishing. Joyful, heartbreaking,
  cutting edge. Brilliantly executed.&rdquo; (<em>The New York Times</em>)
  and "one of the most visually stunning shows to hit New York in ages"
  (<em>USA Today</em>).&nbsp;<br /><br />Don't miss the show that&rsquo;s
  loaded with love, <em>Maybe Happy Ending</em>!</p>
END:VEVENT
